  %div(data-role="content")

    %p
      IPS Strata Solutions was established in September 2009 in Enfield, Sydney. Since then we have serviced clients throughout the Inner West and provide both office and strata cleaning solutions in suburbs from Lane Cove to Hornsby and Epping.

    %p
      We are Occupational Health &amp; Safety aware, trained and compliant. We observe OH&amp;S legislation and regulations to ensure that your property is safe and comfortable for its occupants.

    %p
      Our stringent recruitment process ensures that all cleaners servicing your property are professionally trained to ensure you receive consistently high quality cleaning solutions.
